text: William Babington may refer to: * William Babington (academic), Vice- Chancellor of Oxford University, 1441–1443 * William Babington (justice) (c. 1370–1454), English lawyer and judge * William Babington (physician) (1756–1833), Anglo-Irish physician and mineralogist ==See also== * W. B. Maxwell (William Babington Maxwell, 1866–1938), British novelist * William Babbington, fictional Royal Navy captain in the novels of Patrick O'Brian
title: William Babington
